name: Warning Signs Paperback
description:
Are you looking for love in all the wrong places? Are you being blinded by love? Do you find yourself dating the same type of man over and over again? 

These and other questions will be explored as Danielle guides you through the pitfalls and successes of dating. She will relay stories and examples you can easily relate to. 

**10% of all annual proceeds will support survivors of domestic violence.
